# Screenshots Directory

## Purpose
Visual progress tracking for PFS Shopify theme development.

## Naming Convention
```
section-name-device-state.png

Examples:
hero-integrated-desktop-final.png
hero-integrated-mobile-responsive.png
categories-section-tablet-hover.png
our-best-seller-mobile-progress.png
homepage-full-desktop-complete.png
```

## Categories
- **Desktop:** 1920px, 1366px, 1024px screenshots
- **Tablet:** 768px screenshots  
- **Mobile:** 480px, 375px screenshots
- **States:** normal, hover, loading, error
- **Progress:** wireframe, development, final

## Tools
- Browser dev tools for responsive screenshots
- Full page screenshots for homepage views
- Before/after comparisons for optimizations